title: This 2 bed 1 bath unit is the third floor unit of 1288 Vinton ###
posting_body: This 2 bed 1 bath unit is the third floor unit of 1288 Vinton is located in the historic neighborhood of Central Gardens and has been newly renovated and has water and gas utilities included.
The property features NEW stainless steel appliances (stove), granite counter tops and has laundry on-site.
The property is centrally located in close proximity to all Midtown attractions (Cooper-Young, Overton Square and Minglewood Hall), Downtown and close enough to the interstate for commuters.
